{"title":"Jave内置日志介绍","date":"2020-01-28T09:16:19.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 28, 2020","L":"01/28/2020","MM-DD":"01-28"},"thumbnail":"post/Java/日志/Jave内置日志介绍/cover.jpg","link":"post/Java/日志/Jave内置日志介绍","categories":["Java","日志"],"updated":"2020-02-08T02:39:22.684Z","content":"<h1 id=\"主要组件\">主要组件<a href=\"#主要组件\" title=\"主要组件\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"logger\">Logger<a href=\"#logger\" title=\"Logger\"></a></h2><p>实际使用的日志类。</p>\n<h2 id=\"handler\">Handler<a href=\"#handler\" title=\"Handler\"></a></h2><p>接收日志，并输出到目的地。</p>\n<h2 id=\"filter\">Filter<a href=\"#filter\" title=\"Filter\"></a></h2><p>过滤器，决定一个日志记录是否可以输出。</p>\n<h2 id=\"errormanager\">ErrorManager<a href=\"#errormanager\" title=\"ErrorManager\"></a></h2><p>错误管理器，负责处理<code>Handler</code>处理日志时发生的错误。</p>\n<h2 id=\"logrecord\">LogRecord<a href=\"#logrecord\" title=\"LogRecord\"></a></h2><p>日志记录，每次调用方法输出日志会产生一个该类实例。</p>\n<h2 id=\"logmanager\">LogManager<a href=\"#logmanager\" title=\"LogManager\"></a></h2><p>日志管理器。</p>\n<ul><li>将所有<code>Logger</code>组织成一个层次结构</li>\n<li>维护一些配置信息</li>\n</ul><h2 id=\"level\">Level<a href=\"#level\" title=\"Level\"></a></h2><p>日志级别。</p>\n<ul><li><code>OFF</code></li>\n<li><code>SEVERE</code></li>\n<li><code>WARNING</code></li>\n<li><code>INFO</code></li>\n<li><code>CONFIG</code></li>\n<li><code>FINE</code></li>\n<li><code>FINER</code></li>\n<li><code>FINEST</code></li>\n<li><code>ALL</code></li>\n</ul><h1 id=\"基本使用\">基本使用<a href=\"#基本使用\" title=\"基本使用\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"创建和输出\">创建和输出<a href=\"#创建和输出\" title=\"创建和输出\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">testJavaLogging</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    Logger logger = Logger.getLogger(getClass().getName());</span><br><span class=\"line\">    logger.severe(<span class=\"string\">\"log\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    logger.warning(<span class=\"string\">\"log\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    logger.info(<span class=\"string\">\"log\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    logger.config(<span class=\"string\">\"log\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    logger.fine(<span class=\"string\">\"log\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    logger.finer(<span class=\"string\">\"log\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    logger.finest(<span class=\"string\">\"log\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"todo\">TODO<a href=\"#todo\" title=\"TODO\"></a></h2><p>由于<code>JUL</code>使用不多，不做深入研究。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"maven基本使用","link":"post/Java/Maven/maven基本使用"},"next":{"title":"日志框架迁移","link":"post/Java/日志/日志框架迁移"},"plink":"https://beginc.github.io/post/Java/日志/Jave内置日志介绍/","toc":[{"id":"主要组件","title":"主要组件","index":"1","children":[{"id":"logger","title":"Logger","index":"1.1"},{"id":"handler","title":"Handler","index":"1.2"},{"id":"filter","title":"Filter","index":"1.3"},{"id":"errormanager","title":"ErrorManager","index":"1.4"},{"id":"logrecord","title":"LogRecord","index":"1.5"},{"id":"logmanager","title":"LogManager","index":"1.6"},{"id":"level","title":"Level","index":"1.7"}]},{"id":"基本使用","title":"基本使用","index":"2","children":[{"id":"创建和输出","title":"创建和输出","index":"2.1"},{"id":"todo","title":"TODO","index":"2.2"}]}]}